§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ A ❬convex combination❭ is a linear combination whose sequence
    of scalars is nonnegative and sums to one. ⦉
⦉

§ Characterization ⦉
<statement type='proposition'>
  ‖ A subset of $𝗥^n$ is convex if and only if it contains
    all the convex combinations of its elements. ⦉
</statement>
